    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-grade 2016 Porsche Cayman S, a definitive mid-engine masterpiece featuring the 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six engine. This specimen is mechanically impeccable, equipped with a 6-speed manual gearbox and the Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) system for precision damping. The drivetrain includes a mechanical rear differential lock and Porsche Torque Vectoring (PTV), ensuring optimal turn-in and lateral stability. Braking performance is anchored by four-piston aluminum monobloc fixed calipers over cross-drilled, internally vented rotors. The exterior retains a factory-fresh luster with zero pitting, while the interior showcases pristine Alcantara and leather surfaces. Meticulously maintained with a full service history, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the purist collector seeking peak analog performance.",
