      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, enhanced by a professional ceramic coating with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, and the factory 'new car' scent persists. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history from authorized dealerships and riding on a fresh set of matching high-performance tires. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the driver-assist features, functions perfectly. This is a turn-key, collector-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
